{"id": "1222753107478450258", "channel_id": "1222753107478450258", "type": 0, "author_id": "1189543077648531506", "author_name": "lindongxieyang", "author_bot": false, "content": "我重生了，重生在我买完笔刷的第一天，上辈子我因为买的笔刷太多固定就用那么几个导致我根本没有发现这两个摸鱼很好用的笔刷，大大增加了我的摸鱼时间却进度-50，现在我要重新用这套笔刷拿回属于我的摸鱼时间！\n好了不开玩笑，真的就是买了两笔刷然后摸了个鱼试试，感谢图鲁当我的模特\n线稿：优动漫-赛博签绘-油性笔（湿），铺色笔：秋簌-秋簌水墨基础-写意铺色", "timestamp": "2024-03-28T03:44:18.477000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 16}], "attachments": [{"id": "1222753108279558214", "filename": "-1.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 4263909, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1222753107478450258/1222753108279558214/-1.png?ex=69cbebd2&is=69ca9a52&hm=8721e04a312f5abcd1238c491cdd7178c8a3855f9e0068a9994e30b5816a3086&"}, {"id": "1222753109256962160", "filename": "-1-1.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 7062026, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1222753107478450258/1222753109256962160/-1-1.png?ex=69cbebd2&is=69ca9a52&hm=526ea03fc0e707183e7de01daba00a8f67f5087f0d6f29e4e10e135c6d7bf9cc&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1222753107478450258", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "事情起因只是因为我买了两套新笔刷……", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537"]}
